CPU idle time
item.description: The average time spent by the specified processor doing nothing for the system in the last five mins.

item.name: CPU iowait time
item.description: The average time spent by the specified processor waiting for external I/O to complete for the system in the last five minutes

item.name: CPU interrupt time
item.description: The average time spent by the specified processor servicing hardware interrupts for the system in the last five minutes.

item.name: CPU nice time
item.description: The average time spent by the specified processor running niced processes for the system in the last five minutes.

item.name: CPU softirq time
item.description: The average time spent by the specified processor servicing soft interrupts for the system in the last five mins

item.name: CPU steel time
item.description: The average time 'stolen' from the system in the last five mins

item.name: CPU system time
item.description: The average time spent by the specified processor servicing system calls for the system in the last five minutes.

item.name: CPU average usage ratio
item.description: This is average usage ratio of CPU for the system in the last one minute. It is calculated by (sum of deltas for user, niced, system)/(sum of deltas of user, niced, system, idle, irq, softirq, and iowait), where each delta is the difference for each stat over the last 1-minute interval.

item.name: CPU user time
item.description: The average time spent by the specified processor in user context for the system in the last five minutes.

item.name: sysStatServerCurConns
item.description: The average maximum hardware accelerated connections from server-side to the system in the last five minutes.
